[{"id":"7be8a404f56639f74e7bdb3509a2dd9a","from":"Lookout Mobile Security","from_email":"feedback@email.lookout.com","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Introducing Lookout for Apple Watch","date":"2016-03-10T16:03:41.000Z","formatted_date":"Mar 10, 2016","formatted_time":"4:03 PM","body":" \n\nhttps://click.email.lookout.com/?qs=2e37a6b0bdda678636dca3a77cd6a2c0ef0653970e74c93b5ce367506d00256870f0199d3bbe3781 \n\nWe're thrilled to announce that Lookout is now available for Apple Watch - letting you easily find your iPhone using the Locate and Scream features directly from your wrist. All you need to get started is the latest version of Lookout and an Apple Watch!\n\nhttps://click.email.lookout.com/?qs=b2f9aaa4dc522202f83ff14027f2e26621d3ab88377503423a3dad98d195c7f0b3b878ec39fc15da \nUpdate Lookout Now \n\n\nWith Lookout for Apple Watch, you can:\n\n\n .;\n\nTrack the distance between your iPhone and Watch\n\n\n .;\n\nUse the Scream feature to find your iPhone\n\n\n .;\n\nSee your iPhone\u2019s last recorded location\n\n\n .;\n\nGet an alert if you're about to lose connection &#8212; so you don\u2019t accidentally leave your iPhone behind\n\n\n\nTo get Lookout on your Apple Watch, just update to the latest version of the Lookout iPhone app (4.3) and visit the Watch App Store on your iPhone to switch it on.\n\n\nhttps://click.email.lookout.com/?qs=b2f9aaa4dc522202ee34aed2e97cfab9afd53405efc93306fc7b7dfad2c9c54917ec81d39afd876d \n\nhttps://click.email.lookout.com/?qs=b2f9aaa4dc5222023025ef2a6b549440090a136e91bfd2f3f1a3f84a5e912225b13466d0e823015d \n\n\nSent from Lookout, Inc.\n\n\n1 Front Street Suite 2700\n\n\nSan Francisco, CA 94111\n\n\nhttps://click.email.lookout.com/unsub_center.aspx?qs=3cb13e60d698b9d4c435675ad3bdb6e03026c8cd3f276c269a07f5fbac9aba35966cf1b8d02c26370a1ce758b92258b16ca08cdc65c4903e748c53c265a92a6f \nUnsubscribe \n\n\n\n \n","body_html":"</body></html><html xm